Settings/MarkdownShortcuts: Enable Markdown-style input shortcuts
Settings/MarkdownShortcutsHint: Use Markdown syntax like **bold**, *italic*, ~~strike~~, `code`, # Heading, --- for horizontal rule and ``` for code blocks. Output is always wikitext.
Settings/MarkdownShortcutsAutoForMarkdown: Automatically enable Markdown-style shortcuts when editing Markdown tiddlers
Settings/MarkdownShortcutsAutoForMarkdownHint: Enabled by default for `text/markdown` and `text/x-markdown`. Turn this off if you want Markdown tiddlers to use the same WikiText-oriented shortcuts as other ProseMirror editors.
