Settings/Autocomplete/Caption: Autocomplete
Settings/Autocomplete/DefDescTriggers: Definition description triggers (`:`)
Settings/Autocomplete/DefDescTriggersHint: One trigger per line. Type at the start of a line to create a definition description (<dd>). Default: : and ：
Settings/Autocomplete/DefTermTriggers: Definition term triggers (`;`)
Settings/Autocomplete/DefTermTriggersHint: One trigger per line. Type at the start of a line to create a definition term (<dt>). Default: ; and ；
Settings/Autocomplete/Description: Configure trigger characters for autocompletion of links, transclusions, and macros
Settings/Autocomplete/LinkTriggers: Link triggers (`[[`)
Settings/Autocomplete/LinkTriggersHint: One trigger per line. Type these characters to open link autocompletion. Default: [[ and 【【
Settings/Autocomplete/MacroTriggers: Macro triggers (`<<`)
Settings/Autocomplete/MacroTriggersHint: One trigger per line. Type these characters to open macro autocompletion. Default: << and 《《
Settings/Autocomplete/TransclusionTriggers: Transclusion triggers (`{{`)
Settings/Autocomplete/TransclusionTriggersHint: One trigger per line. Type these characters to open transclusion autocompletion. Default: {{ and 「『
